legend_materias.name: Superiority Complex
legend_materias.description: Begin battle temporarily infused with the power of lightning.

soul_strikes.name: Reverse Gaia
soul_strikes.description: Deal fifteen physical wind and non-elemental attacks to one enemy, temporarily infuse the user with the power of wind, temporarily grant the user Awoken Thief Mode, increase the user's Cap Break Level by 1, and increase the amount thief abilities charge the user's Soul Break gauge a moderate amount.

awake_explanations.description_text: Grant unlimited use of thief abilities, grant up to a moderate Thief Ability Boost, and cause the user's thief abilities to trigger twice.

soul_strikes.extensive_description: Deal fifteen physical wind and non-elemental attacks to one enemy, temporarily infuse the user with the power of wind, temporarily grant the user Awoken Thief Mode, increase the user's Cap Break Level by 1, and increase the amount thief abilities charge the user's Soul Break gauge a moderate amount.
